                <Header/>
                <Paragraph>The "Guide to Federal Records in the National Archives of the United States" indicates that records of the organizations in the Executive office of the President  have been assigned to record group 429. Within that record group, the records of the Citizens' Advisory Committee on Environmental Quality (CACEQ) are located in subgroup 429.3. The CACEQ was established on May 29, 1969, and its members advised the newly established Environmental Quality Council.</Paragraph>
